        <head>Lose this child</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>Lose this child </l>
          <l>He’s in your arms </l>
          <l>Lose this child </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>Who’s in charge? </l>
          <l>It’s in your mind </l>
          <l>Lose this child </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>Send it to the sky </l>
          <l>Save it in your smile </l>
          <l>Send it to the moon </l>
          <l>Say it like you don’t care </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>Send it to the sky </l>
          <l>Save it for a while </l>
          <l>Send it to the moon </l>
          <l>Say it like you’re not there </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="5" type="stanza">
          <l>Fools to try to spill my wine </l>
          <l>Are they blind?</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
